### Tactical Context
**Requirements**: [Key requirements identified]
**Design Decisions**: [Major design decisions made]
**Architecture**: [System architecture planned]

### Implementation Plan
**Phases**: [List of implementation phases]
**Priorities**: [Task priorities and dependencies]
**Timeline**: [Expected timeline for completion]

### Ready for Operational Execution
**Todos Created**: [Number of todos created]
**Dependencies**: [Any dependencies or blockers]
**Success Criteria**: [How success will be measured]

### Handoff Status
**Date**: [Timestamp]
**Tactical Work Complete**: [Yes/No]
**Ready for Operational Mode**: [Yes/No]
```

## 🚀 **TACTICAL MODE COMMANDS**

```
🎨 "tactical" or "plan" → Enter Tactical Mode
📋 "requirements" → Analyze requirements
🎨 "design" → Make design decisions
📊 "plan" → Create implementation plan
📝 "todos" → Create or update todos
🔄 "handoff" → Prepare handoff to Operational Mode
```

